n: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">UN:&nbsp;</strong><span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">1208</span><br style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\"><strong style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">CAS:</strong><span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">&nbsp;110-54-3&nbsp;</span><br style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\"><br style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\"><strong style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">Place of delivery:</strong><span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">&nbsp;According to the necessity of the client.</span>', '', '', '', '', '', 'hexano1354223480.jpg', 'hexano_eng1354224974.jpg', '', ''),
(17, 'Nafténica Media', '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">La principal aplicación de las bases lubricantes es la manufactura de aceites lubricantes tanto para uso en automotores (aceite tipo cárter) como para usos en la industria. Las bases nafténicas se utilizan preferentemente en la elaboración de lubricantes para bajas temperaturas y con mayor fluidez.&nbsp;</span>', 'Naphthenic Medium', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">The most common use of these lubricant bases is for oils and for automotive use, (carter type oil) and also for industrial use. The naphthenic bases are preferably used in the fabrication of lubricants that are used in low temperatures and higher flows.</span>', 3, '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">También se usan como materia prima para la fabricación de tintas, vaselinas o como agentes ablandadores del fique.&nbsp;</span>', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">They are also used as raw material for the production of ink, Vaseline and as plasticizers of sisal.&nbsp;</span>', '', '', '', '', '', 'base_parafinica_media1354226468.jpg', 'base_parafinica_media_eng1354226468.jpg', '', ''),
(18, 'Nafténica Pesada', '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(99,=\\"\\" 99,=\\"\\" 99);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">La principal aplicación de las bases lubricantes es la manufactura de aceites lubricantes tanto para uso en automotores (aceite tipo cárter) como para usos en la industria. Las bases nafténicas se utilizan preferentemente en la elaboración de lubricantes para bajas temperaturas y con mayor fluidez.</span>', 'Heavy Naphthenic', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">The most common use of these lubricant bases is for oils and for automotive use, (carter type oil) and also for industrial use. The naphthenic bases are preferably used in the fabrication of lubricants that are used in low temperatures and higher flows.</span>', 3, '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(99,=\\"\\" 99,=\\"\\" 99);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">También se usan como materia prima para la fabricación de tintas, vaselinas o como agentes ablandadores del fique.</span>', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">They are also used as raw material for the production of ink, Vaseline and as plasticizers of sisal.&nbsp;</span>', '', '', '', '', '', 'base_naftenica_pesada1354226272.jpg', 'base_naftenica_pesada_eng1354226272.jpg', '', '');
