(19, 'Parafínica Liviana', '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(99,=\\"\\" 99,=\\"\\" 99);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">La principal aplicación de las bases lubricantes es la manufactura de aceites lubricantes tanto para uso en automotores (aceite tipo cárter) como para usos en la industria. Las bases Parafínicas son preferidas para la fabricación de aceites de alto índice de viscosidad.</span>', 'Light Paraffinic', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">The most common use of these lubricant bases is for oils and for automotive use, (carter type oil) and also for industrial use. Paraffinic bases are preferred in the production of oils with high viscosity index levels.</span>', 3, '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(99,=\\"\\" 99,=\\"\\" 99);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">También se usan como materia prima para la fabricación de tintas, vaselinas o como agentes ablandadores del fique.</span>', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">They are also used as raw material for the production of ink, Vaseline and as plasticizers of sisal.&nbsp;</span>', '', '', '', '', '', 'base_parafinica_liviana1354226239.jpg', 'base_parafinica_liviana_eng1354226239.jpg', '', ''),
(20, 'Parafínica Media', '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(99,=\\"\\" 99,=\\"\\" 99);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">La principal aplicación de las bases lubricantes es la manufactura de aceites lubricantes tanto para uso en automotores (aceite tipo cárter) como para usos en la industria. Las bases Parafínicas son preferidas para la fabricación de aceites de alto índice de viscosidad.</span>', 'Medium Paraffinic', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">The most common use of these lubricant bases is for oils and for automotive use, (carter type oil) and also for industrial use. Paraffinic bases are preferred in the production of oils with high viscosity index levels.</span>', 3, '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(99,=\\"\\" 99,=\\"\\" 99);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">También se usan como materia prima para la fabricación de tintas, vaselinas o como agentes ablandadores del fique.</span>', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">They are also used as raw material for the production of ink, Vaseline and as plasticizers of sisal.&nbsp;</span>', '', '', '', '', '', 'base_parafinica_media1354226211.jpg', 'base_parafinica_media_eng1354226211.jpg', '', ''),
(21, 'Parafínica Bright Stock', '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(99,=\\"\\" 99,=\\"\\" 99);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">La principal aplicación de las bases lubricantes es la manufactura de aceites lubricantes tanto para uso en automotores (aceite tipo cárter) como para usos en la industria. Las bases Parafínicas son preferidas para la fabricación de aceites de alto índice de viscosidad.</span>', 'Bright Stock Paraffinic', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">The most common use of these lubricant bases is for oils and for automotive use, (carter type oil) and also for industrial use. Paraffinic bases are preferred in the production of oils with high viscosity index levels.</span>', 3, '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(99,=\\"\\" 99,=\\"\\" 99);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">También se usan como materia prima para la fabricación de tintas, vaselinas o como agentes ablandadores del fique.</span>', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">They are also used as raw material for the production of ink, Vaseline and as plasticizers of sisal.&nbsp;</span>', '', '', '', '', '', 'base_parafinica_bright1354226138.jpg', 'base_parafinica_bright_eng1354226152.jpg', '', ''),
(22, 'Polifén 640', '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\&quot;color:\\\\&quot;\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" 141,=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" 141);=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" font-family:=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" font-size:=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" 14px;=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" line-height:=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" 20px;=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" text-align:=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" justify;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\">La principal aplicación de las bases lubricantes es la manufactura de aceites lubricantes tanto para uso en automotores (aceite tipo cárter) como para usos en la industria. Las bases nafténicas se utilizan preferentemente en la elaboración de lubricantes para bajas temperaturas y con mayor fluidez.</span>', 'Polifén 640', '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">As a resin for the extrusion sheets in the processes of injection and blow molding- It is used in the production of bags with medium resistance, liquid medications containers, sheets for agricultural and construction use.&nbsp;</span>', 4, '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\&quot;color:\\\\&quot;\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" 141,=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" 141);=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" font-family:=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" font-size:=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" 14px;=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" line-height:=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" 20px;=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" text-align:=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\" justify;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\">También se usan como materia prima para la fabricación de tintas, vaselinas o como agentes ablandadores del fique.</span>', '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">It possesses medium optical properties and an excellent resistance towards any ruptures.</span>', '', '', '', '', '', 'polifen_6401354224847.jpg', 'polifen_640_eng1354224847.jpg', '', ''),
(23, 'Polifén 641', 'Resina para extrusión de películas de múltiple uso, diseñada para utilizarse donde se requieran buenas propiedades mecánicas y ópticas. Se emplea para bolsas de supermercados, panadería, alimentos, forros de cuadernos y otros usos. \r\n<br><br>\r\n  \r\n', 'Polifén 641', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">It’s a resin used for the extrusion of multi-purpose sheets, it is also designed to be used wherever good optical and mechanical properties are needed. It is used for supermarket bags, bakery bags, notebook covers and it has other uses.&nbsp;</span>', 4, 'También se utiliza para fabricar bolsas semiindustriales y empaques de alimentos en procesos de sellado automático solo o en conjunto con resinas de última tecnología, dependiendo del nivel de exigencia de las empacadoras.<br>\r\n<br>', '<span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">It is also utilized for the fabrication of semi-industrial bags and food packaging processes with automatic seals; these are done with top of the line technology depending on the demand of packaging companies.</span>', '', '', '', '', '', 'polifen_6411354224882.jpg', 'polifen_641_eng1354224882.jpg', '', ''),
(24, 'Ceras parafínicas', '<span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">Descripción: Las ceras Parafínica, o sencillamente parafinas, son una mezcla de hidrocarburos saturados (enlaces sencillos entre carbonos) de cadena lineal, cuyo peso molecular oscila entre 320 y 560, y presentan consistencia sólida a temperatura ambiente. Se obtiene a partir de fracciones de la destilación al vacío de crudo reducido (fondos de la destilación atmosférica) con rango de destilación entre 350 y 650 °C, las cuales se someten a procesos de dilución con solvente, enfriamiento regulado, cristalización y filtración para separar las parafinas de los aceites.&nbsp;</span>', 'Paraffinic Waxes', '<strong style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">Description:</strong><span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">&nbsp;Paraffin is a mix of saturated hydrocarbons (simple linkages between carbons) of lineal chains, whose molecular weight ranges between 320 and 560; they exhibit a solid consistency in room temperature. This wax is obtained through fractions that come from the fractions that are produced through the vacuum-reduced crude distillation, with a range of distillation between 350° and 650°C. Paraffin undergoes a dilution with a solvent, regulated cooling, crystallization, and filtration, to separate all the paraffin from the oil.</span>', 5, '<strong style=\\"\\\\&quot;margin:\\" 0px;=\\"\\" padding:=\\"\\" border:=\\"\\" outline:=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" vertical-align:=\\"\\" top;=\\"\\" color:=\\"\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">Precauciones para el manejo:</strong><span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">&nbsp;Deben almacenarse en recipientes limpios y cerrados, y alejados de posibles fuentes de combustión.</span><br style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\"><br style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\"><strong style=\\"\\\\&quot;margin:\\" 0px;=\\"\\" padding:=\\"\\" border:=\\"\\" outline:=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" vertical-align:=\\"\\" top;=\\"\\" color:=\\"\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">Uso:</strong><span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">&nbsp;La principal aplicación de las parafinas es la manufactura de velas y productos relacionados. En menor proporción se utilizan para la fabricación de cera para pisos, papeles parafinados, fósforos, vaselinas, recubrimiento de alimentos y otros usos industriales.&nbsp;</span><br style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\"><strong style=\\"\\\\&quot;margin:\\" 0px;=\\"\\" padding:=\\"\\" border:=\\"\\" outline:=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" vertical-align:=\\"\\" top;=\\"\\" color:=\\"\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">UN</strong><span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">: 1223</span><br style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\"><strong style=\\"\\\\&quot;margin:\\" 0px;=\\"\\" padding:=\\"\\" border:=\\"\\" outline:=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" vertical-align:=\\"\\" top;=\\"\\" color:=\\"\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">CAS:</strong><span style=\\"\\\\&quot;color:\\" rgb(141,=\\"\\" 141,=\\"\\" 141);=\\"\\" font-family:=\\"\\" avantgardemdbtmedium;=\\"\\" font-size:=\\"\\" 14.44444465637207px;=\\"\\" line-height:=\\"\\" 20px;=\\"\\" text-align:=\\"\\" justify;\\\\\\"=\\"\\">&nbsp;8002-74-2&nbsp;</span>', '<strong style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: AvantGardeMdBTMedium; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;\\">Precautions of Handling:</strong><span style=\\"color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-family: